{"tid":1653503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"修例風波：龍翔道檢61支汽油彈　疑針對紀律部隊宿舍","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T09:15:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":165,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":136,"replies":[{"pid":"18645767bb95bfe28378ca3aaa60258fcd8391ca","tid":1653503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"反修例風波延續，示威者所使用的武力愈見升級，今晨(14日)9時許，有市民在龍翔道近馬仔坑遊樂場一處草地發現一箱可疑物品，於是報警。<br />\n警員到場視察，發現草地上一個紙皮箱內裝有61支懷疑汽油彈，探員隨即將其檢走作進一步檢驗，初步不排除擬有人針對黃大仙紀律部隊宿舍，惟該批汽油彈的來源及確實用途有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191014/bkn-20191014131205404-1014_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191014%2Fbkn-20191014131205404-1014_00822_001.html&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=9eb29f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191014/bkn-20191014131205404-1014_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c04df62a738ab99731a7338d5c26558e5d7653b","tid":1653503,"uid":21545,"like":207,"dislike":7,"score":200,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"邊位臥底留底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b84d4e66797b5929d9c40b22075e7f1080ae6e9","tid":1653503,"uid":108337,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"又自編自導自演"},{"pid":"bffd9bdf24405b6432dbbaa23e10f380b7541cd5","tid":1653503,"uid":66488,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"自己擺？"},{"pid":"a5dfb73c65c77de454fb2f05036b419761173459","tid":1653503,"uid":210612,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"有就掉晒啦"},{"pid":"f2b8c910e96146a41714b9d1390bc9398106dccc","tid":1653503,"uid":176545,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a5dfb73c65c77de454fb2f05036b419761173459","tid":1653503,"uid":210612,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":3,"replyTim